data.description: Welcome to this cute 3-bed, 2-bath home in Stephenville a great affordable price point! Most of the home was remodeled in 2019. Step inside to discover a well-designed floor plan that maximizes space and functionality. The heart of the home is a cozy living area, providing a warm and inviting atmosphere for relaxation or entertainment. Well-equipped kitchen with lots of cabinet space. 2 bedrooms are oversized, offering plenty of room! Conveniently close to downtown and right on the walking trail! This will make the perfect starter home or college rental.
